WEBVTT

00:01:27.668 --> 00:01:30.146
Nikakuta kwamba wengi
wako katikati -

00:01:30.170 --> 00:01:31.636
kati ya kutoa na kupokea.

00:01:31.660 --> 00:01:34.005
Hawa huchagua mtindo wa tatu "kulipiza."

00:01:34.029 --> 00:01:37.374
Walipizaji huweka
usawa kati kutoa na kupokea:

00:01:37.398 --> 00:01:40.716
nipe nikupe --nitakusaidia ukinisaidia.

00:01:40.740 --> 00:01:43.121
Inaonekana kama namna salama ya kuishi.

00:01:43.145 --> 00:01:46.329
Ila, je, ni njia fanisi ya kuishi?

00:01:46.353 --> 00:01:48.817
Jibu la hakika kwa swali hilo, ni

00:01:48.841 --> 00:01:49.999
labda.

00:01:50.023 --> 00:01:51.249
(Vicheko)

00:01:51.273 --> 00:01:53.452
Nimechunguza mashirika kadhaa,

00:01:53.476 --> 00:01:54.651
maelfu ya watu.

00:01:54.675 --> 00:01:58.227
Nmepima tija miongoni wahandisi.

00:01:58.251 --> 00:02:00.606
(Vicheko)